Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Meet the neighbours
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w82d
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 Mar 1981
Reagan in talks with Trudeau while southerly foreign policy - regarding El Salvador - is softened. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less